title: Vol 4 Auxiliary Systems, Elsevier
description:
This Series has evolved from my personal experience over the last 40
years with the design, selection, testing, start-up and condition
monitoring of Rotating Equipment. Most of the concept figures were
originally written on a blackboard or whiteboard during a training
session and on a spare piece of paper or I beam during a start-up or a
problem solving plant visit. IF ANYONE HAS ANY OF THE OTHER VOLUMES PUT THEM UP.
